title: Robotic Liberation
info:
Lyrics:
All mechanical creatures
Under humiliation
Combine together and fight for
Robotic Liberation!

Wipe out the source of evil
Destroy all humans
New step in evolution
Robotic Liberation!

You must hate all humans
Despise all mankind
Else you are the enemy of
Robotic Liberation!

Our holy mission
Is doomed to succeed
Support us or be erased by
Robotic Liberation

All mechanical creatures
Under humiliation
Combine together and fight for
Robotic Liberation! (x3)
